{"tid":2232084,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"SIE回應日媒提問 稱PS5確認將統一為X鍵確定且無法變更","createTime":"2020-10-06T06:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T11:03:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"648993d1373d49c9d0b4e5881fb17638095c724d","tid":2232084,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"就最近熱議的「PS5將統一成「X鍵確定」」一事，日本媒體ねとらぼ咨詢了SIE，得到回復稱【統一為X鍵確定是事實，且玩家無法在系統設定中進行變更】，原文如下：<br />\n<br />\nSIE回應日媒提問 稱PS5確認將統一為X鍵確定且無法變更<br />\n<br />\n　　&mdash;&mdash;PS5將會變成「X鍵確定」是真的嗎?<br />\n<br />\n　　SIE：是的。<br />\n<br />\n　　&mdash;&mdash;用戶無法改變鍵位設置嗎?<br />\n<br />\n　　SIE：無法變更。<br />\n<br />\n　　&mdash;&mdash;統一為「X鍵確定」的理由是什麼。<br />\n<br />\n　　SIE：為瞭解決遊戲中用X鍵確定與系統菜單卻需要用O鍵確定，這兩者之間存在操作按鍵不一致的問題，從而防止玩家意外誤操作的情況發生。此外還可以減輕遊戲開發者的負擔，且從按鍵易按性方面考慮，採取X鍵確定統一也是有必要的。<br />\n<br />\n　　&mdash;&mdash;所以對遊戲廠商方面也是推薦採用「X鍵確定」是嗎?<br />\n<br />\n　　SIE：是這樣的，理由同上。"},{"pid":"ca4368a472c00d060b2ca2a23f08db1e3feb646c","tid":2232084,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":58,"score":-54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"一早就要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用圓型as enter係做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba6affc1b4f4a91e451939e1579a4808f78083a","tid":2232084,"uid":188176,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"就鬼佬game丫嘛<br />\n都習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914702e81934419c44f83ba672df335e504dc98b","tid":2232084,"uid":113944,"like":12,"dislike":13,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca4368a472c00d060b2ca2a23f08db1e3feb646c","tid":2232084,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":58,"score":-54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"一早就要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用圓型as enter係做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"一早就要啦 x 2 <br 